data.description: Antibacterial ball pen with push-up mechanism. Monochromatic design and soft body in solid white with original curved clip, especially designed for pad printing. Blue ink refill. Item according to the ISO 22196 standard, which determines the antibacterial activity in plastic materials and non-porous surfaces. This allows us to know the effectiveness of microbial inhibition that additives have on treated objects by means of a quantitave evaluation.
